Digicon Inc offering exchange 55 mln dlrs outstanding subordinate debenture package issues. The outstanding debenture issue include 12-7/8 pct senior subordinate note 10-1/2 pct convertible subordinate debenture 8-1/2 pct convertible subordinate debenture unit Digicon Finance NV. The security issue exchange offer 8.5 mln dlrs 12 pct senior subordinate note due 1994 23.5 mln dlrs 9.35 pct convertible subordinate debenture due 1997 16.5 mln share common stock. Reuter 